EC - Class in cinvestav.android.pki.cryptography.algorithm
This class implements the common functions for EC like encrypt (ECIES), decrypt (ECIES), keyGen, sign (ECDSA), verify (ECDSA) using the SouncyCastle API (http://rtyley.github.com/spongycastle/)
